24
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,660
would he have gotten away?

25
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,650
Can we still find his house?

26
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:08,520
Why not?

27
00:01:08,950 --> 00:01:10,680
Who doesn't go home after work?

28
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,560
