30
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:18,680
He still has to go home
after dinner, right?

31
00:01:18,950 --> 00:01:19,680
What if he goes for a bath

32
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,690
after dinner?

33
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,070
He still has to go home

34
00:01:24,070 --> 00:01:25,330
