43
00:01:42,509 --> 00:01:44,789
If he doesn't go home
and goes for a foot wash the day after,

44
00:01:44,789 --> 00:01:46,789
we'll follow him the day after that.

45
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,130
Does he have that many activities?

46
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,789
No matter how many activities he has,

47
00:01:50,789 --> 00:01:52,350
