52
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:00,870
Then...

53
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:28,010
[Born with Luck]

54
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:31,050
[Episode 8]

55
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,800
Since you guys grew up together,

56
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,000
