57
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,130
doesn't make sense.

58
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,770
Why did you report Zhou Rong then?

59
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:41,400
Because of love.

60
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,870
Hello, Yibo.

61
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,850
Hello, Qi.

62
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,000
There's a new movie out recently.

63
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,910
Do you want to go see it?

64
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:54,710
I'm not going.

65
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:55,750
