74
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,480
This is too much.

75
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:52,330
[report letter]

76
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,000
This is too much.

77
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,000
Then nobody gets to live.

78
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,500
Nobody gets out alive.

79
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,320
Then nobody gets to live!

80
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,150
I am a police officer.

81
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,360
Don't run to this area!

82
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,560
It's dangerous here!

83
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,710
I am a cop!

84
00:05:20,530 --> 00:05:22,440
[I hereby report this under my real name.]

85
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,480
The name is

86
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:22,430
