126
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,510
But the whole world knows

127
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,870
I can't stand the smell of leeks.

128
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:28,560
My mouth

129
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,960
