163
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,630
and once verified,

164
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:03,870
-you can get your parcel back.
-I…

165
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:04,650
I'm at

166
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,750
Yiyuan Haoting residential community.

167
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:07,450
Where is

168
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:08,620
