170
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,150
Hurry up, okay?

171
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:12,600
Please wait a moment, sir.

172
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,800
I'll check it for you.

173
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,030
So

174
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:31,120
