went to the provincial capital.

175
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,430
You chased it to the provincial capital

176
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:34,090
to get the report letter back.

177
00:09:35,650 --> 00:09:36,320
Your package

178
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,870
