179
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:38,600
Don't worry.

180
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:40,130
I have the package with me.

181
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,670
You can bring your ID to find me,

182
00:09:41,670 --> 00:09:42,840
or wait at the station.

183
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,510
No need.

184
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,200
I'll go to you.

185
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,000
I'll go to you.

186
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:47,420
[Name: Lu Yibo]

187
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:46,550
Is it you?

188
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:47,320
On behalf of the organizers

189
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,360
