192
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,320
Great!

193
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,320
Eight!

194
00:09:53,390 --> 00:09:54,270
Seven!

195
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,440
Six!

196
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,240
Five!

197
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,510
Four!

198
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,750
Three!

199
00:09:59,080 --> 00:09:59,910
Two!

200
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,600
One.

201
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,240
Believe it or not,

202
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:08,890
I'm telling the truth.

203
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,600
I can swear to God.

204
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,480
Then why did you write
in the report letter

205
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,120
that he was related to

206
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,360
Lu Zheng's death?

207
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:17,040
Because when Lu Zheng died,

208
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,200
I acted on impulse

209
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:20,550
and wanted to frame him

210
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:21,360
with a felony.

211
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,510
But the case

212
00:10:23,630 --> 00:10:25,270
had already been officially settled.

213
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,270
That's why I wrote the report letter

214
00:10:26,270 --> 00:10:27,400
to you, Chief Zhang.

215
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:29,210
Everyone in Sanjiangkou knows

216
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,750
