219
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,750
Your...

220
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:40,840
According to what you're saying now,

221
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:43,100
you and Zhou Rong are childhood friends,

222
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:45,360
