223
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,600
and the letter contains

224
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,000
some fatal accusations.

225
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:49,270
Now you're telling me

226
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,200
none of these are true

227
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,720
and it's a misunderstanding.

228
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,780
This hardly dispels our suspicions.

229
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:57,160
It's also out of envy and jealousy.

230
00:10:57,790 --> 00:10:58,150
Yes.

231
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,550
We are childhood friends.

232
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,150
Mr. Rong,

233
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,270
Ye,

234
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,270
Bowen,

235
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:03,200
and I.

236
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,480
But I actually hate them.

237
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,770
What do you mean?

238
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:11,720
Not to mention Mr. Rong.

239
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,980
He's the boss of Rongcheng Group,

240
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,720
a famous entrepreneur in Sanjiangkou.

241
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,650
It should be him.

242
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:18,480
Bowen is doing well these years.

243
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,940
He's making a lot of money.

244
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,910
Before Ye died, he was the captain

245
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:23,150
of Sanjiangkou CID.

246
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:24,910
He had a successful career

247
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:26,000
and power.

248
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,440
Who takes me seriously?

249
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,390
Aren't you a somebody?

250
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:28,850
Wait,

251
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,510
I'm just saying at least you are

252
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:32,000
the general manager
of Fenglinwan Hotel.

253
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,330
You have a big business.

254
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,640
You only see the surface.

255
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,200
I'm just an employee.

256
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:41,120
Fenglinwan Hotel was invested by Mr. Rong.

257
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,720
I'm just his legal representative

258
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,000
earning a fixed salary.

259
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,500
You are the legal representative
of his company?

260
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:48,030
This is not illegal, right?

261
00:11:48,210 --> 00:11:50,010
Then according to what you said,

262
00:11:50,870 --> 00:11:53,600
you also hold a grudge against
Ye Jian, don't you?

263
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:55,570
I hate myself more.

264
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,150
I'll tell you something

265
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:04,390
