268
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:10,370
to write down three words.

269
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:11,720
It's a name.

270
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,270
There's a "Yi" in the middle.

271
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:17,840
Chief Zhang,

272
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,750
