273
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:20,790
Ye

274
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,880
couldn't have written my name.

275
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:25,170
It doesn't make sense.

276
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,080
You know enough already.

277
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:31,840
One last question for you.

278
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,970
Answer truthfully.

279
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:33,680
Go ahead.

280
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,360
The night Ye Jian was murdered,

281
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,160
