282
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,870
Fenglinwan is an entertainment venue.

283
00:12:38,870 --> 00:12:39,910
To avoid suspicion,

284
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:43,110
-he didn't even come to the opening.
-Answer my question.

285
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,390
No.

286
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,480
Lu Yibo

287
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:02,570
is definitely not telling the truth.

288
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,600
But he didn't look like

289
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,550
