290
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,090
Chief Zhang,

291
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,210
how about we find some time

292
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:14,410
to invite Zhou Rong
to the station for questioning?

293
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:17,600
Lu Yibo only admitted

294
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,960
that the person he reported was Zhou Rong.

295
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:22,790
Now he says he was smearing Zhou Rong.

296
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,000
He also took the report letter back.

297
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,130
We have no evidence.

298
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,500
Calling Zhou Rong in like this

299
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,340
would just tip him off.

300
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,360
Could Zhou Rong already know

301
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:38,600
about Lu Yibo writing the report letter?

302
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,750
Definitely not.

303
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,460
Think about it, Chief.

304
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:42,690
If Zhou Rong knew

305
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,920
Lu Yibo reported him,

306
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:45,600
he would skin him alive.

307
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:47,030
Could he still sit there

308
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:47,830
drinking tea?

309
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:49,320
We finally

310
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,580
found a breakthrough.

311
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,300
And now it's closed again.

312
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:01,480
Chief Zhang.

313
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:02,700
Wang.

314
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:04,390
Good evening, officers.

315
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,060
Let's go, Wang.

316
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,940
No, maybe she's just

317
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:15,770
being polite.

318
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,510
Before we came,

319
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,610
didn't you say

320
00:14:35,910 --> 00:14:36,750
that the night gave you

321
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:37,720
dark eyes?

322
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,130
But I use them to look for the light.

323
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,670
So where is the light?

324
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,330
Lu Yibo insists on denying it.

325
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,480
The report letter
doesn't constitute evidence.

326
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,990
Ye has never been to Fenglinwan Hotel.

327
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:48,720
Chief Zhang,

328
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:50,280
how do we investigate this?

329
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:55,470
Keep moving forward,

330
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:58,870
constantly pursuing that golden hope.

331
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,790
I still think

332
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:12,240
that Lu Yibo's report letter

333
00:15:12,270 --> 00:15:14,130
appearing at the explosion scene

334
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,840
is too much of a coincidence.

335
00:15:16,370 --> 00:15:21,400
♪ Doubt ♪

336
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,910
It can't be a coincidence

337
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:21,790
that this report letter was found

338
00:15:21,790 --> 00:15:23,120
at the explosion scene.

339
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:29,620
♪ Doubt ♪

340
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,550
Is it possible

341
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:30,600
that someone wanted to
stop Lu Yibo from delivering the letter,

342
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,060
even trying to blow him up?

343
00:15:32,710 --> 00:15:47,920
Doubt, Doubt, Doubt

344
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:38,080
We need to check the files
on the provincial capital explosion.

345
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:39,480
These two incidents

346
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,480
shouldn't be connected, right?

347
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:43,480
Check the files
on the provincial capital explosion.

348
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,790
Mr. Rong, are you still mad at me?

349
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,480
Are you done?

350
00:15:57,630 --> 00:15:59,490
Mr. Rong doesn't want to kill you.

351
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:00,590
Ren,

352
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,360
stop joking around.

353
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:05,480
We are driving out of Sanjiangkou.

354
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:07,360
Can you find

355
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,390
a nice and scenic place

356
00:16:08,390 --> 00:16:09,450
before you kill me?

357
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:18,110
To tell you the truth:

358
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:20,030
Mr. Rong wants to give you

359
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:22,090
a chance to make up for your mistakes.

360
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:23,880
What do you want me to do?

361
00:16:25,990 --> 00:16:27,840
Do you know anything about music?

362
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,900
What kind of music?

363
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,150
Percussion

364
00:16:30,510 --> 00:16:31,440
with drumbeats.

365
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:35,790
Mr. Lang!

366
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:37,360
Mr. Lang,

367
00:16:38,170 --> 00:16:39,360
you walk so fast.

368
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:40,990
I had a hard time catching up.

369
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:42,070
This is...

370
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:43,600
This is your...

371
00:16:44,150 --> 00:16:44,630
My what?

372
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:47,970
Bill for this month.

373
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:53,600
So I have to pay

374
00:16:53,630 --> 00:16:55,630
when I come to Fenglinwan Hotel now?

375
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:56,720
No, Mr. Lang.

376
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:59,480
The store has been losing money.

377
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:00,480
This is a new rule.

378
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:02,190
Just sign it for me.

379
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:03,260
Where is Lu Yibo?

380
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:04,510
Mr. Lu?

381
00:17:05,589 --> 00:17:06,770
I haven't seen him. I don't know.

382
00:17:06,770 --> 00:17:07,460
Call him.

383
00:17:07,510 --> 00:17:08,839
Let him tell me himself.

384
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,400
Mr. Lang,

385
00:17:10,589 --> 00:17:12,720
please don't make it difficult for me.

386
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:13,810
Qi.

387
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,650
Ask her if you don't believe me.

388
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:17,500
Come here.

389
00:17:19,550 --> 00:17:21,220
Mr. Lang, what's wrong?

390
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,140
Let's chat.

391
00:17:22,250 --> 00:17:23,150
Let's chat.

392
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:24,609
Let me see the bill.

393
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:25,510
Okay.

394
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,230
How could you not know

395
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:29,810
where Lu Yibo went?

396
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:30,590
Officer,

397
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,210
Yibo is a guy

398
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:34,040
who really likes to play around.

399
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:34,870
He plays games

400
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,200
and goes fishing.

401
00:17:36,270 --> 00:17:37,400
When he's having fun,

402
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,750
it's common for him to disappear

403
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:40,110
for two or three days.

404
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:43,510
You can't reach him for a couple of days.

405
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:45,580
Don't move.

406
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,960
Just sign it.

407
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,350
If you can contact him,

408
00:17:49,350 --> 00:17:50,690
tell him we came looking for him.

409
00:17:50,690 --> 00:17:51,510
There are still a few details

410
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:54,240
about the provincial capital case
we need to confirm with him.

411
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,250
Okay, officer.

412
00:17:55,370 --> 00:17:56,830
We won't bother you anymore.

413
00:17:56,830 --> 00:17:57,960
Take care, officer.

414
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:08,290
Hello. The number you have dialed

415
00:18:08,290 --> 00:18:09,450
-is powered off.
-Qi.

416
00:18:09,450 --> 00:18:11,560
Sorry, the subscriber you dialed

417
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,450
is powered off.

418
00:18:12,510 --> 00:18:13,200
Wen?

419
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:24,590
Why are the police

420
00:18:24,790 --> 00:18:25,880
looking for Yibo?

421
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:28,970
Yibo and I

422
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,660
grew up together as brothers.

423
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:33,240
Is there anything you can't tell me?

424
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:35,380
Wen,

425
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:37,750
tell me,

426
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:39,590
if Yibo did something

427
00:18:39,590 --> 00:18:40,920
to let Mr. Rong down,

428
00:18:42,070 --> 00:18:44,000
but he truly realized his mistake,

429
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,730
would Mr. Rong forgive him?

430
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:49,430
What do you mean by that?

431
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:52,770
I don't know anything.

432
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,070
Tell me

433
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,270
what exactly Yibo did?

434
00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:00,800
How did he let Mr. Rong down?

435
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:14,080
This is your last chance.

436
00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:16,040
If you mess it up,

437
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:17,400
I will really find you

438
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,070
a picturesque place to bury you.

439
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:19,730
Don't, bro.

440
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,170
Go.

441
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:25,510
Before the matter is done,

442
00:19:25,510 --> 00:19:26,770
don't contact anyone.

443
00:19:28,110 --> 00:19:29,110
Is it that simple?

444
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,000
It is that simple.

445
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:44,880
Ren,

446
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:45,790
what's Zhu Yifei's background

447
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:46,820
anyway?

448
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:48,070
Am I in any danger?

449
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:49,780
Ren!

450
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:50,870
Ren!

451
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:07,930
Is anyone here?

452
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,060
Is anyone here?

453
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,920
Only the dog is home.

454
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,680
Who are you looking for?

455
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,160
Hello,

456
00:20:21,110 --> 00:20:23,440
I'm from Rongcheng Group
in Sanjiangkou.

457
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:24,240
No, no, no.

458
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,240
I'm here to buy something from Uncle Fei.

459
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,200
Ren arranged it.

460
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:45,480
[Huo Zheng — Zhu Yifei's subordinate]

461
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:45,810
Is it turned off?

462
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,830
I turned it off on the way here.

463
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:49,280
Don't mind it, brother.

464
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:52,410
It's just the rules of the game.

465
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,630
Wait here.

466
00:21:28,510 --> 00:21:29,070
Sir.

467
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:31,520
Sir.

468
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,320
Excuse me,

469
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:35,680
do they sell chimes here?

470
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:41,910
Uncle Fei.

471
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:43,930
Fish food.

472
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:46,010
Are you Zhu Yifei?

473
00:21:46,550 --> 00:21:47,550
Yes.

474
00:21:46,870 --> 00:21:49,820
[Huo Zheng — Zhu Yifei's subordinate]

475
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:49,890
But we are

476
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:51,380
legitimate businessmen.

477
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:56,350
The goods you want

478
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:58,460
are not available.

479
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:01,880
Sorry for making you come for nothing.

480
00:22:07,540 --> 00:22:09,740
Brother, please give me the phone back.

481
00:22:10,030 --> 00:22:10,920
It's mealtime.

482
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:13,160
Let's eat together.

483
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,790
I'll pass on the meal.

484
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:20,900
Business may fail, but friendship remains.

485
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:22,750
If I don't invite you to stay for a meal,

486
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:23,750
and word gets out,

487
00:22:25,310 --> 00:22:27,000
they'll say I have no manners.

488
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:38,030
Hello?

489
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:39,590
Did you see the goods?

490
00:22:39,590 --> 00:22:40,110
No.

491
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:42,600
Then why are you still there?

492
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,110
Boss Zhu invited me to eat.

493
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:47,690
How about

494
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,480
you come here yourself, Ren?

495
00:22:52,070 --> 00:22:52,550
Ren?

496
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:55,440
Eat, Yibo.

497
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:57,790
It was Mr. Rong who gave you the chance

498
00:22:57,790 --> 00:22:59,050
to negotiate the deal.

499
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:06,020
Turn off the phone.

500
00:23:08,550 --> 00:23:09,410
Hello, it's me.

501
00:23:09,550 --> 00:23:10,210
Hu Jianren,

502
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:12,160
is Zhu Yifei reliable?

503
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,350
I know he hasn't failed

504
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:16,480
all these years.

505
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,400
It's just that if the deal falls through,

506
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,590
no one gets out.

507
00:23:20,590 --> 00:23:21,640
But I just want to know

508
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:23,400
if he has the goods right now.

509
00:23:29,910 --> 00:23:30,390
Uncle,

510
00:23:31,070 --> 00:23:33,440
it's been a long time.

511
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,730
It should be about time.

512
00:23:36,550 --> 00:23:39,750
Now is the perfect time
to simmer the soup.

513
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:42,130
Since they are here,

514
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:44,630
they can't leave empty-handed.

515
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:46,350
What if they only want the chime bells

516
00:23:46,350 --> 00:23:47,350
and nothing else?

517
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,120
Then for the next pot,

518
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,300
we'll simmer them.

519
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:06,900
Black tiger palm mushroom
and chicken soup.

520
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:07,820
Have a taste

521
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:09,170
while it's hot.

522
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:20,750
That's the taste.

523
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:23,780
To be honest,

524
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:26,960
it's my first time eating tiger paw.

525
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:29,690
Whether it's the right taste,

526
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:30,760
I don't know.

527
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:33,320
But it's a really good soup.

528
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:41,640
Tigers

529
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:43,040
are national treasures.

530
00:24:43,350 --> 00:24:44,820
Do you really think

531
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:45,750
I'd chop off a tiger's paw

532
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:46,880
just to make soup

533
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:47,970
for you?

534
00:24:48,310 --> 00:24:49,910
I'd rather stew you instead.

535
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:54,920
Just kidding.

536
00:24:56,110 --> 00:24:57,510
This is a kind of mushroom

537
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,010
called Black Tiger Paw.

538
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:02,000
Understand?

539
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,550
Then this is just

540
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:08,510
ch- chicken stewed with mushrooms?

541
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:09,410
Let me tell you,

542
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,920
this kind of fungus

543
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,250
is extremely precious.

544
00:25:12,750 --> 00:25:13,440
Its price

545
00:25:13,590 --> 00:25:15,540
isn't necessarily cheaper

546
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,640
than a real tiger paw.

547
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:17,970
But the soup made from it

548
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:20,200
is even more delicious
than a real tiger paw.

549
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:20,930
Try it again.

550
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:29,650
Young man.

551
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:32,040
There are some things in this world

552
00:25:32,470 --> 00:25:33,680
that you can't force.

553
00:25:34,830 --> 00:25:36,480
There is always a substitute.

554
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:36,920
Right?

555
00:25:38,310 --> 00:25:38,790
Yes.

556
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:18,670
Thank you.

557
00:26:19,790 --> 00:26:20,250
Well...

558
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:21,370
What are you doing?

559
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:24,240
This...

560
00:26:24,790 --> 00:26:25,880
Wh- What's wrong?

561
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:33,440
What's wrong, young man?

562
00:26:34,830 --> 00:26:36,400
Do you know what this is?

563
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,070
Ru kiln porcelain.

564
00:26:41,930 --> 00:26:43,090
Ru kiln porcelain?

565
00:26:44,550 --> 00:26:46,150
It was from the Song Dynasty.

566
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,480
Only 67 pieces have survived

567
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:51,510
in the entire world to this day.

568
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:53,400
And you actually

569
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:55,270
spit bones into it.

570
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:59,440
Are you going to sell this to Mr. Rong?

571
00:27:02,510 --> 00:27:04,030
Is this one of those

572
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:04,760
67 pieces?

573
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:06,110
This is

574
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,230
the 68th piece.

575
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:10,310
Not long ago,

576
00:27:10,350 --> 00:27:11,750
a friend of mine

577
00:27:12,590 --> 00:27:14,590
salvaged a sunken ship
from the Song Dynasty

578
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:17,550
in the Indian Ocean.

579
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:19,240
This item

580
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:21,750
was found in the ship.

581
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,540
[Ping'an Province
Antique Appraisal Center.]

582
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:27,060
It's the appraisal certificate
issued by experts.

583
00:27:28,980 --> 00:27:31,370
[Provenance: Northern Song Dynasty]

584
