746
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:41,110
Zhengzheng, see him out.

747
00:33:41,110 --> 00:33:42,400
Don't.

748
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:43,180
I don't know the market.

749
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:44,510
I don't know the market.

750
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:46,720
