756
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:00,030
Thr...

757
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,830
300 million?

758
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:04,440
I'm doomed.

759
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,270
I'm completely doomed.

760
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:07,170
I'm doomed.

761
