796
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:38,920
Whose fault is it?

797
00:35:39,150 --> 00:35:41,280
Put it down first.

798
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,190
Gently.

799
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,190
Put it down.

800
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:45,550
