810
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,400
I have to put it down,

811
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,400
and you pick it up yourself.

812
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:13,760
Understand?

813
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,510
Understood.

814
00:36:36,550 --> 00:36:37,000
Uncle.

815
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:42,880
