829
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:16,110
If worse comes to worst,

830
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:17,050
let's find a fool

831
00:37:17,150 --> 00:37:18,610
and sell it to him cheaper.

832
00:37:20,710 --> 00:37:21,670
Call someone

833
00:37:21,670 --> 00:37:22,550
