834
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:25,090
Tell him to come here

835
00:37:25,110 --> 00:37:25,960
right now.

836
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:28,000
I heard

837
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,230
