840
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:35,670
Liu Bei.

841
00:37:47,890 --> 00:37:50,890
[Liu Bei — tomb raider]

842
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,320
Thanks, Uncle.

843
00:37:53,230 --> 00:37:53,920
Bei,

844
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:56,800
I heard

845
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,880
