846
00:38:03,150 --> 00:38:03,880
Chime bells?

847
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:09,320
And it's a complete set.

848
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:10,530
A complete set.

849
00:38:11,230 --> 00:38:12,070
