852
00:38:18,190 --> 00:38:19,000
I know.

853
00:38:20,230 --> 00:38:22,490
I've been holding onto it for half a year.

854
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,000
Uncle,

855
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:29,470
