859
00:38:41,110 --> 00:38:43,360
I'll figure something out.

860
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:47,840
But the goods must be authentic.

861
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:49,760
I'll go get it for you right now.

862
00:38:52,510 --> 00:38:52,920
Uncle.

863
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:55,160
