878
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,230
to Zhou Rong.

879
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:19,430
How much?

880
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:21,280
You think I want to?

881
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:23,740
The plate was broken for nothing?

882
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,190
I'm going to sell it to him for double.

883
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:27,450
Isn't double

884
00:39:27,670 --> 00:39:29,240
only 40 million?

885
00:39:29,550 --> 00:39:30,760
There's also the brothers' share.

886
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,110
They can't work for free.

887
00:39:32,110 --> 00:39:33,800
Do you have any compassion?

888
00:39:39,550 --> 00:39:41,230
You always think of everything, Uncle.
